start-dialogue-0: Isn't the entrance to Kaohsiung Harbor Museum gorgeous?
start-dialogue-1: Did you notice the windows on either side of the entrance are different?
start-dialogue-2: The museum is open until 5 PM on weekdays!
start-dialogue-3: The Kao Port Park is right behind the museum, I recommend checking it out!
start-dialogue-4: Hehe! Doesn't this hat make me look smart?
start-dialogue-5: Baroque architecture is usually very grand and ornate, full of artistic flair!
